EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   17 THRU 21 SEP IN AREA WITHIN 52 MILES OF
   57-26.5N 008-47.0W. VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER
   AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 212000Z SEP 18.
